title: NC State baseball smoked by Virginia Tech 21-10 in series opener - N.C. State University Technician Online
content: NC State baseball smoked by Virginia Tech 21-10 in series opener  N.C. State University Technician Online
description: The No. 21 NC State baseball team got smoked by the Virginia Tech Hokies 21-10 in the series opener in Blacksburg, Virginia on Friday, April 8.
